headline: 3 Accident & Health Insurers Navigating High Medical Costs, Inflation
summary: Accident and Health Insurance stocks like GL, TRUP and EIG are set to gain from rising underwriting exposure and accelerated digitalization. However, pricing pressure is a concern given rising medical costs and inflation.
